<span id="freeTextContainer14143796335386966404">4.5 Stars<br/><br/>Candice has to be one of the most refreshing &amp; honest female leads I have ever read. I adore her lack of perfection, and her comfort in her own skin. Just phenomenal. She was the highlight of this book. The romance was so fun. The whole book was just wonderfully unexpected. Definitely lived up to the first!</span>

