  <span id="freeText17077260808967807285" style="display:none"><b> <i> 5 "Candice is hilarious" stars! </i></b> <br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1382462243ra/5902047.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>For the second time <i> Elle Casey </i> made me <b> LAUGH OUT </b> countless times!<br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1400092249ra/9633903.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>This book was <b> FUNNY </b> , <u> sexy </u> and soooo much <i> entertaining </i>!<br>I couldn't hide my smile ever since the beginning of the book! I knew it was going to be good because we've met the MCs in the previous book and there we saw that they will <b> match </b> just well!<br>I was waiting for them to see that they were ment to be <u> together </u>!<br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1419390819ra/13056092.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><b> Candince </b> was <i> AMAZING HEROINE </i>! So funny, sweet, caring and wanted to help everyone with everything she can! She may be vain or high maintenance but these things only made her more precious! She was <b> badass </b>, I will give her that! Buying a gun, saving a life, caring for an animal.. she couldn't deny that she was <b> into </b> the country life! She was brave and nothing couldn't stop her when she wanted somehing! Plus her innder monologues here <b> THE BEST </b>!<br><br><blockquote>
<b> <i> “Do not look at his package, Candice. Do not look at his package. My eyes move of their own accord. Oh dammit, you looked at his package! And … oh my … Oh my, my, my … There’s a giant bulge! Hooray for giant bulges and the jeans that let me see them!” </i></b> </blockquote><br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1438943435ra/15772645.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>I loved her because she wanted to help her bestfriend to feel safe and good! She would do everything to make that happen and I felt related to her about that! What is more beautiful than to care about the people you love and wanted them to feel safe and happy whenever they are?! <br>Everyone in the town saw that it's for the best if the don't piss <b> Candice </b> off!<br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1438943435ra/15772646.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><blockquote>
<b> <i>“You are not just one person, Candice. You’re a whole tornado of a person.” </i></b> </blockquote><br><br><b> Candince &amp; Ian </b> helped each other! They heald each other in the best way! Their banters were <i> AMAZEBALLS </i>! They slow building sexual tension and chemisery were <i> off charts </i>! They couldn't deny their connection and besdies <b> INSTALOVE </b> is something I love <i> very much </i> and these books provided me a <u> a hell of instalove </u> and bunch of sweet &amp; sexy timessss!<br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1438943435ra/15772647.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><b> Ian </b> was so sweet beside his broody mood! He wanted to find the woman who will complete him and <i> oh, boy </i> he did! He was <u> sexy and funny! </u> Caring and charming! He loved her with his whole heart and all he wanted was to look after her and love her! He <b>melted</b> my heart !!!!<br><br><blockquote>
<b><i>“Babe, I can’t promise you that I’ll always be perfect, but I’ll do my straight best to try, and I’ll make it my life’s goal to always make sure you’re happy. All you’ve got to do is marry me, and I’ll do the rest.” </i></b> </blockquote><br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1438943435ra/15772648.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>If you want a book without much drama and a book which will leave you with the <b> biggest smile </b> after you finish it - <i> This is the book! </i>!</span>
