<li class='cover' id='bookCover_55105569'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/55105569-amici"><img alt="Amici" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1598298741l/55105569._SX98_.jpg" />
